        "message": "Patch Set 1: Code-Review-1\n\nI would propose editing the backoff only in tests:\nFile: org/onap/dcae/collectors/veshv/config/impl/test_constants.kt\n\n internal fun retry(iterationCount: Long = 1) = Retry\n        .onlyIf<Any> { it.iteration() <= iterationCount }\n        .fixedBackoff(Duration.ofNanos(1))\n\nIn the production code the backoff for retrySpec in CbsConfigurationProvider is set by the class creating the CbsConfigurationProvider object and its set to exponential backoff.",
